communicate any schedule changes...

1733
00:19:37,786 --> 00:19:39,788
...on the day of the Athletics Festival directly

1734
00:19:39,788 --> 00:19:41,856
to the person in charge of each post.

1735
00:19:41,856 --> 00:19:43,024
If I try to say it with words,

1736
00:19:43,024 --> 00:19:44,674
I might screw up again.

1737
00:19:54,803 --> 00:19:56,653
If I'm going to get hurt...

1738
00:19:59,541 --> 00:20:01,841
...I want Arima to be the first one.

1739
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:12,539
What'll happen next!

1740
00:22:12,907 --> 00:22:14,457
Sis finally became an
official couple with him!

1741
00:22:14,457 --> 00:22:19,180
But harsh reality brings
new trials and enemies!

1743
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:20,648
When will happiness

1744
00:22:20,648 --> 00:22:21,983
